eeded changing for some reason... so I changed it! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />  The xvalue is <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">currScreen</tt>.  Oh, and helpJoe is here... <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">0E0BC&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;helpJoe: ;this should help our screens to be all level!<br />0E0BC 00 00 00 10 20 30&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;.db 0, 0, 0, $10, $20, $30</div><br /><br />edit: I fixed my code... it said &quot;<s>;this helps Joe, the x value</s>&quot;...</div>

